  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard Glide is an experimental fast-paced arcade game with inertial mouse control only (but you can also use a gamepad or mouse+WASD). A small fragile bot has been awakened among the bizarre world of machines, driven by the commands of the mysterious Mainframe, he must overcome increasingly difficult levels filled with a variety of hostile bots and dangerous obstacles, and fulfill his main Goal. This is what his Program says. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/b5e3c03f2e6cd65c4fd06c4cf9eb7baf.poster.avif?t=1739533913\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/b5e3c03f2e6cd65c4fd06c4cf9eb7baf.webm?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/b5e3c03f2e6cd65c4fd06c4cf9eb7baf.mp4?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The controls in the game are a little unusual, but quite simple:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >move the mouse to control the movement of your character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >press and hold down the left mouse button to shoot and lock the sight in one direction, regardless of the movement direction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >while shooting, you can rotate the sight on 180 degrees by pressing the right mouse button</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >transferring objects (keys) and moving platforms at transit stations also occurs by holding down the left mouse button </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >if you need a hint where the level goals are, just click on the middle mouse button (wheel)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/876085639770fdc7fc700f88095a45ab.poster.avif?t=1739533913\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/876085639770fdc7fc700f88095a45ab.webm?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/876085639770fdc7fc700f88095a45ab.mp4?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When creating this game, I was inspired by arcade games of the past, I tried to get closer to the same adrenaline-pumping gameplay experience, but with the addition of modern graphics and effects. The game is aimed at those players who love action games of dexterity and skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/68e3fdebdf8f526959dab6c7209128ca.poster.avif?t=1739533913\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/68e3fdebdf8f526959dab6c7209128ca.webm?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/68e3fdebdf8f526959dab6c7209128ca.mp4?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard Glide is an experimental fast-paced arcade game with inertial mouse control only (but you can also use a gamepad or mouse+WASD). A small fragile bot has been awakened among the bizarre world of machines, driven by the commands of the mysterious Mainframe, he must overcome increasingly difficult levels filled with a variety of hostile bots and dangerous obstacles, and fulfill his main Goal. This is what his Program says. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/b5e3c03f2e6cd65c4fd06c4cf9eb7baf.poster.avif?t=1739533913\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/b5e3c03f2e6cd65c4fd06c4cf9eb7baf.webm?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/b5e3c03f2e6cd65c4fd06c4cf9eb7baf.mp4?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The controls in the game are a little unusual, but quite simple:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >move the mouse to control the movement of your character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >press and hold down the left mouse button to shoot and lock the sight in one direction, regardless of the movement direction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >while shooting, you can rotate the sight on 180 degrees by pressing the right mouse button</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >transferring objects (keys) and moving platforms at transit stations also occurs by holding down the left mouse button </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >if you need a hint where the level goals are, just click on the middle mouse button (wheel)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/876085639770fdc7fc700f88095a45ab.poster.avif?t=1739533913\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/876085639770fdc7fc700f88095a45ab.webm?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/876085639770fdc7fc700f88095a45ab.mp4?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When creating this game, I was inspired by arcade games of the past, I tried to get closer to the same adrenaline-pumping gameplay experience, but with the addition of modern graphics and effects. The game is aimed at those players who love action games of dexterity and skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/68e3fdebdf8f526959dab6c7209128ca.poster.avif?t=1739533913\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/68e3fdebdf8f526959dab6c7209128ca.webm?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731390/extras/68e3fdebdf8f526959dab6c7209128ca.mp4?t=1739533913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
